title: Cool Cool
description: A hidden vegetarian restaurant known for its stinky tofu, one of a few rare specialties. No English signboard or menu, just Chinese or Khmer; if you don't speak either, point at the pictures. Set meals come with rice, pickles, one type of mock meat, fried tofu, and fried veggies or a clear soup - cost is around US$3-5. Air conditioned. Apr 2014 reported still open.
